article.description: — Jeenathan Williams had 28 points and 12 rebounds as Buffalo got past Towson 74-65 on Friday.
article.headline: Williams carries Buffalo past Towson 74-65
article.story: UNCASVILLE, Conn. -- — Jeenathan Williams had 28 points and 12 rebounds as Buffalo got past Towson 74-65 on Friday. Jayvon Graves added 20 points six rebounds and five steals and Brock Bertram had 12 rebounds and four blocks for Buffalo (1-0). Josh Mballa added eight rebounds. Zane Martin had 27 points and six assists for the Tigers (0-3). Charles Thompson added 17 points and Victor Uyaelunmo had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
